{"parentUuid":"1e396eb1-7887-4769-bdf1-d344d3d3ff5c","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"/home/admin/.openclaw/workspace/projects/2026-03-10_recruitment-aggregator","sessionId":"33b86ee2-d4bf-4648-8011-635e7aa76683","version":"2.1.71","gitBranch":"master","message":{"id":"05feb6b9b6ac9113c372dcbe201d6a7c","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我需要设计一个合理的架构。对于爬虫项目，需要考虑：\n1. 模块化设计 - 分离不同招聘平台的爬虫\n2. 数据存储 - 使用数据库或文件存储\n3. 数据处理 - 清洗、过滤AI相关公司\n4. API接口 - 提供数据查询接口\n\n让我创建详细的架构设计文档。","signature":"79172feda9a226798de495abe62845c0704157737edfa46531695f38eca05715"}],"model":"MiniMax-M2.1","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3167,"output_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":17499},"service_tier":"standard"},"type":"assistant","uuid":"a1d29be2-73db-408c-bee0-00c23af461ae","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:36:45.270Z"}
{"parentUuid":"a1d29be2-73db-408c-bee0-00c23af461ae","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"/home/admin/.openclaw/workspace/projects/2026-03-10_recruitment-aggregator","sessionId":"33b86ee2-d4bf-4648-8011-635e7aa76683","version":"2.1.71","gitBranch":"master","message":{"id":"05feb6b9b6ac9113c372dcbe201d6a7c","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"call_function_u7nhs0pnqqah_1","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/admin/.openclaw/workspace/projects/2026-03-10_recruitment-aggregator/ARCHITECTURE.md","content":"# 招聘数据聚合器 (info-collector)\n\n## 项目架构设计\n\n### 1. 项目结构\n\n```\ninfo-collector/\n├── src/\n│   ├── __init__.py\n│   ├── main.py                 # 入口文件\n│   ├── config.py               # 配置管理\n│   ├── models/                 # 数据模型\n│   │   ├── __init__.py\n│   │   └── job.py              # 职位数据模型\n│   ├── crawlers/               # 爬虫模块\n│   │   ├── __init__.py\n│   │   ├── base.py             # 基类\n│   │   ├── maimai.py           # 脉脉爬虫\n│   │   └── boss.py             # Boss直聘爬虫\n│   ├── processors/             # 数据处理\n│   │   ├── __init__.py\n│   │   └── filter.py           # AI公司过滤\n│   ├── storage/                # 数据存储\n│   │   ├── __init__.py\n│   │   └── json_storage.py     # JSON文件存储\n│   └── utils/                  # 工具函数\n│       ├── __init__.py\n│       └── logger.py           # 日志工具\n├── tests/                      # 测试\n├── CLAUDE.md                   # AI入口\n├── README.md\n├── requirements.txt\n└── .gitignore\n```\n\n### 2. 核心功能\n\n- **多平台爬取**: 脉脉、Boss直聘\n- **AI公司过滤**: 识别AI公司及相关产业链（芯片、算法、数据、算力等）\n- **数据存储**: JSON格式本地存储\n- **去重**: 基于公司和职位名称去重\n\n### 3. 数据模型\n\n```python\nJob:\n  - source: str           # 来源平台\n  - title: str            # 职位名称\n  - company: str         # 公司名称\n  - location: str        # 工作地点\n  - salary: str           # 薪资范围\n  - description: str      # 职位描述\n  - requirements: str    # 任职要求\n  - posted_date: str      # 发布日期\n  - url: str              # 原始链接\n  - timestamp: str       # 抓取时间\n```\n\n### 4. 关键词过滤\n\nAI公司关键词：\n- AI、人工智能、机器学习、深度学习\n- 大模型、LLM、AIGC、ChatGPT\n- 芯片、半导体、GPU、TPU\n- 云计算、算力、数据服务\n- 自动驾驶、智能驾驶\n- 机器人、无人机\n- 智慧城市、智能硬件\n"}}],"model":"MiniMax-M2.1","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":3167,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":17499,"output_tokens":681,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"service_tier":"standard"},"type":"assistant","uuid":"86a77982-72c2-4a54-948f-9062e66f532c","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:36:56.223Z"}
